    "dcterms:abstract": [
        {
            "@language": "ja",
            "@value": "異才、後藤ひろひとが仕掛けた罠…伝説の衝撃を超える震撼のラスト！\r\n\r\n笑いの扉を開けると、底なしの恐怖が、待っていた…\r\n\r\n売れない童話作家の平川(成河)が披露する奇想天外な童話に、近所の子供たちは大はしゃぎ。\r\nけれども、童話の登場人物や題名はレスラーの名前、テーマも\"三流大学出身より高卒の方がまし\"だから、子どもの親からはクレームばかり。\r\n公園に集まる子供たちの中には、へんてこ童話の主人公になりきって現れる奇妙な青年・サム(加藤諒)がいた。\r\nある日、平川はひょんなことからTVタレントのアキラ(ミムラ)と知り合う。その出会いは平川の作風にも大きな変化をもたらしていくのだが…",
            "is_public": true,
            "property_id": 19,
            "property_label": "Abstract",
            "type": "literal"
        },
        {
            "@language": "en",
            "@value": "A trap set by the brilliant Goto Hirohito…\r\nThe last of the tremors which surpass the legendary shock!\r\n\r\nWhen opening the door of laughter, there awaited a bottomless horror…\r\n\r\nThe neighborhood children are beyond excited by the strange fairy tales presented by Hirakawa (Songha), an unsuccessful fairy tale writer. \r\nHowever, the names and titles of the characters appearing in the stories of those of wrestlers, and the themes are that “it is better to be just a high school graduate than graduating from a third-rate university”, so there are many complaints from the parents of the children.\r\nAmong the children who gather in the park is the strange youth Sam (Kato Ryo) who appears as the main character of the weird fairy tale.\r\nOne day, Hirakawa encounters the TV personality Akira (Mimura) by chance. That encounter brings about a big change in Hirakawa’s style, but…",
            "is_public": true,
            "property_id": 19,
            "property_label": "Abstract",
            "type": "literal"
        }
    ],
